--- !u!114 &1689029836
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 1689029834}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: e939807b669dc4e7f8275d4d57f9837f, type: 3}
  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::NPC
  npcName: Argos
  relationshipGain: 5
  dialogueLow: Get out of my workshop. I have no time for people like you.
  dialogueNeutral: I'm Argos. I don't talk much. If you want to learn, watch and
    work.
  dialogueFriendly: You've got good hands. Not many people do anymore.
  dialogueClose: Forty years I've worked this forge. You're one of the few I'd trust
    to carry it on.
  dialogueFestivalGeneric: A good festival means good commissions afterward. People
    want to commemorate.
  dialogueCityDionysia: 
  dialogueThargelia: 
  dialoguePanathenaia: 
  dialogueHephaestia: Hephaestus made the shield of Achilles himself. On his festival
    I remember why I chose this craft.
  dialogueThesmophoria: 
  dialoguePyanopsia: 
  dialogueLenaia: 
  dialogueHaloa: 
  interactionRadius: 0.5
  timeCostMinutes: 30
  conversationCooldownSeconds: 10
  promptUI: {fileID: 734620836}
  romancePromptUI: {fileID: 826962097}
